Third-Party Notices
===================

Nerd Fonts
----------

This project includes data and font assets from Nerd Fonts:

- Glyph index data in `data/nerd-font-glyphs.json` is generated from Nerd Fonts' generated CSS at `https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts/gh-pages/_includes/css/nerd-fonts-generated.css`.
- Preview rendering uses `data/fonts/SymbolsNerdFontMono-Regular.ttf`, downloaded from Nerd Fonts.

Nerd Fonts licensing is described at `https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts/blob/master/LICENSE`.

The Nerd Fonts license states that original source code files and source files not in folders containing an explicit license are under the MIT License:

```text
The MIT License (MIT)

Copyright (c) 2014 Ryan L McIntyre
```

The generated glyph index is derived from Nerd Fonts' generated CSS and is distributed with attribution to Nerd Fonts and Ryan L McIntyre.

The bundled preview font is distributed under the license included with that font at `data/fonts/LICENSE`.
